cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SE. 

The paper is about optimizing the computation of Answer Set Programming (ASP), which is a subfield of logic programming and nonmonotonic reasoning. Therefore, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of heuristics and tree-decomposition techniques, which are related to cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper proposes an approach for integrating the optimization algorithm into an ASP system, which is related to cs.SE (Software Engineering).
